OL,3,CThousands of rail fare prosecutions
OL,4,Cset to be declared void
OL,6,FThousands of prosecutions for alleged
OL,7,Ffare evasion brought by train
OL,8,Fcompanies are set to be declared void
OL,9,Fafter a judge's ruling.
OL,11,FFour companies, including Northern
OL,12,FRail and Greater Anglia, brought
OL,13,Fprosecutions against thousands of
OL,14,Fpassengers using the single justice
OL,15,Fprocedure (SJP), despite not being
OL,16,Fpermitted to do so.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/18
