OL,3,CThousands of rail fare prosecutions
OL,4,Cset to be declared void
OL,6,FGiving a summary of his judgment, he
OL,7,Fsaid: "Parliament did not envisage
OL,8,Fthese offences being prosecuted
OL,9,Fthrough the SJP.
OL,11,F"They should never have been brought
OL,12,Fthrough that process. This is, to my
OL,13,Fmind, a paradigm nullity."
OL,15,FHe continued: "I'm satisfied that the
OL,16,Fcorrect approach is to declare each of
OL,17,Fthe prosecutions void and a nullity."
OL,19,FWhat is the single justice procedure
OL,20,Fand what is it for?
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/18
