OL,6,FThe single justice procedure (SJP) was
OL,7,Fintroduced in 2015 to make the legal
OL,8,Fprocess more accessible, speedy and
OL,9,Fefficient.
OL,11,FIt means a single magistrate with a
OL,12,Flegally qualified adviser can try
OL,13,Fminor, non-imprisonable offences
OL,14,Fwithout a court hearing, unless the
OL,15,Fdefendant chooses to attend.
OL,17,FIt can be used if the defendant has
OL,18,Feither pleaded guilty, or not
OL,19,Fresponded, to notification of
OL,20,Fprosecution.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/18
