OL,6,FMore than 500,000 SJP cases were heard
OL,7,Fin magistrates' courts in England and
OL,8,FWales in 2020.
OL,10,FThe system has been criticised for not
OL,11,Fbeing adequately transparent, with it
OL,12,Fhappening largely behind "closed
OL,13,Fdoors".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/18
