OL,6,FJudge Goldspring said "the number
OL,7,Fseems to change every time I ask", but
OL,8,Fa figure of "over 74,000" is a "best
OL,9,Fguess at the moment".
OL,11,FThursday's ruling only affects the six
OL,12,F"test cases", with the judge putting
OL,13,Fin motion plans for the thousands of
OL,14,Fother prosecutions to be declared void
OL,15,Fin the same way.
