OL,6,FFollowing his ruling, he said attempts
OL,7,Fwould be made by HM Courts and
OL,8,FTribunals Service, the Department for
OL,9,FTransport and the train operating
OL,10,Fcompanies to identify those affected
OL,11,Fin the coming weeks.
OL,13,FHe said a list of those affected would
OL,14,Faim to be compiled by the end of
OL,15,FSeptember, with the cases listed as a
OL,16,F"bulk" hearing "by the end of October".
