OL,6,FHe said: "I will simply list them as a
OL,7,Fbulk listing, no parties required, and
OL,8,Fthen I will then make a similar
OL,9,Fdirection in relation to all these
OL,10,Fcases affected, so everybody is in the
OL,11,Fsame position."
OL,13,FThe judge said by the end of November,
OL,14,F"a team will be out in place to begin
OL,15,Fthe work of recovering the money paid
OL,16,Fand refund the money to individuals".
OL,18,F"There are discussions ongoing with
OL,19,Fall the parties about how that may be
OL,20,Fpaid," he added.
